        <p id="link2">LAUNCH</p>
        <h5>/qbot [query]"..."</h5>
        <p style="color:black">searches our database for the best answer to your coding question.</p>
        <h5>/qbot [quick query]"..."</h5>
        <p style="color:black">searches and returns the top 3 queries from google.</p>
        <h5>/qbot [koan]</h5>
        <p style="color:black">/qbot returns a random Zen Koan.<br><br>ko·an<br>
noun<br><br>
a paradoxical anecdote or riddle, used in Zen Buddhism to demonstrate the inadequacy of logical reasoning and to provoke *enlightenment.<br><br>*Help our minds with any coding road blocks.  </p>
        
          
